Policy.acknowledgement_statement: The Southern Community Cohort Study, the Nashville Breast Health Study, the Southern Tri-state Breast Health Study were supported, in part, by NIH grants U01CA202929, R01CA100374, and U54CA91405, respectively. The Southern Tri-state Breast Health Study was also supported by funds for the Anne Potter Wilson Chair endowment. from Vanderbilt University. The Ghana Breast Health Study was supported in part by funding from the NCI intramural research program.
